{"tid":1364603,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（最後心意）我已為李鵬同志準備咗悼詞.........","createTime":"2019-07-25T11:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:16:30.000Z","uid":16365,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d460334561e3fef736f32f7d146db200247a965e","tid":1364603,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:40:30.000Z","msg":"心情未平伏......見到大家願意為李鵬同志舉辦悼念會......花咗啲時間準備咗份悼詞..., 盡量精簡咗...略盡綿力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">李</span>傑星沉</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鵬</span>翔鳳翥</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死</span>而不朽</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">德</span>厚流光</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">浩</span>氣長存！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翥：讀「主」<br />\n鳳翥鵬翔意指奮發有為...<br />\n德厚流光指人道德高，影響深遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家社會撕裂，為確保其他人唔會誤會我哋有其他目的，請大家帶埋花去......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有其他悼詞嘅話，都可以喺下面繼續貼...<br />\n<br />\n希望李同志安息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gRKCL8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgRKCL8y.png&h=04ce785a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d02d5738a08004b4057a82b4080af02e82693ca","tid":1364603,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f6bc7c203b4f5542abef9fef22c7806ab31093","tid":1364603,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef147defaeb618eb0cebc25ea55af7c6cb78d6ad","tid":1364603,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345b34fee824a6bba7c30aeac6e05c6e81e6742a","tid":1364603,"uid":16365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"好心痛<br />\n我的國<br />\n那麼強"},{"pid":"fb1938e8f589dcf960e673d332eed9b9284b47b5","tid":1364603,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"悼念要拎花。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994679663c24d2b2583d253b313d9bb2d5f963d3","tid":1364603,"uid":199012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奠而泣"},{"pid":"ee6b4e361df68345adfd86e2b732d268d2ac9d49","tid":1364603,"uid":172599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"李老味西死得好呀"},{"pid":"64d2d6f75947776b9ffade8a86034ed77eff3775","tid":1364603,"uid":263221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6e894fca990a925cd722a4cc6830179cf5f830","tid":1364603,"uid":202730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fb1938e8f589dcf960e673d332eed9b9284b47b5","tid":1364603,"uid":16365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:43:51.000Z","msg":"悼念要拎花。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撚比花佢啦"},{"pid":"41d4999667f3a2728c4610c4da7b206eb3b33696","tid":1364603,"uid":17220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"哭了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd29489a08c4a0e08c642936be765d72c8eccd1","tid